<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>• ضعفه الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ. <span class="c2">«الميزان»</span> ٣ <span class="c2">(٦٣٨٢)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
